<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="intensity-n">intensity <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪn'tensəti/    美 /ɪn'tensəti/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>强烈；剧烈；激烈：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The intensity of the hurricane was frightening.
飓风的强烈程度令人恐惧。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He spoke with great intensity.
他言辞激烈。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[术语] 强度；烈度：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>varying intensities of natural light
自然光不断变化的强度</p></div></div>